{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"faa5d5d9d3","title":"关于工会的右派言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1ea86fbc75","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"faa5d5d9d3"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1384fa7998","name":"张文石"},{"id":"43b6bf1199","name":"王韶唐"},{"id":"4c1fd609fe","name":"汪志光"},{"id":"ea25ac8f66","name":"西北农学院"},{"id":"ec603a3174","name":"马国庆"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"17422ccab6","type":"title","text":"关于工会的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"faa5d5d9d3"},{"id":"c4b0cc062e","type":"authors","text":"西北农学院王韶唐张文石汪志光马国庆","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"faa5d5d9d3"},{"id":"764d7437e6","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“工会与民主党派是维护官僚主义的。”(化学系副教授　王韶唐)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"faa5d5d9d3"},{"id":"56d49d98b6","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“关于工会我认为只是历来一张大布告、或给小组长下通知，再另外就是交会费，工会在各项学习运动中没起啥作用，以我看来工会是可有可无的组织。”(图书馆　张文石)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"faa5d5d9d3"},{"id":"d19bf8b78f","type":"paragraph","text":"3．“工会与人事方面一样完全是尾巴主义。”(图书馆　汪志光)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"faa5d5d9d3"},{"id":"12190fb481","type":"paragraph","text":"4．“工会这几年完全是尾巴主义，如遇着啥问题，跟着党放马后炮。如某些同志犯错误后，党政一处理，马上工会就嗷嗷叫开了，也是开除会员。事前不给党政提出任何材料，事后也不去分析研究，证实材料，只是当尾巴。”(图书馆　马国庆)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"faa5d5d9d3"},{"id":"503d3f403e","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《西北农学院右派言论及错误言论汇集》(西北农学院马列主义教研组编印，1957年12月)。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"faa5d5d9d3"}],"page":{"id":"2b2cb2b6af","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"faa5d5d9d3","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}